course_title: Studies in Latin Prose and Verse - LATN PROSE&VERSE

sections.comments: Topic: Cicero and his Reputation. Mostly prose readings with some verse. Visit cnrs.ubc.ca for full course descriptions.Cross-listed with LATN 403A. Please check cnrs.ubc.ca or contact the instructor for web-based course delivery information.

description: Advanced thematic studies using both Latin prose and Latin verse. May be repeated for up to 6 credits.
